CustomField.formula: IF(ISPICKVAL(Work_Overtime_Frequency__c ,"Weekly"), Work_Overtime_amount__c *52, IF(ISPICKVAL(Work_Overtime_Frequency__c ,"Fortnightly"), Work_Overtime_amount__c *26, IF(ISPICKVAL(Work_Overtime_Frequency__c ,"Monthly"), Work_Overtime_amount__c *12, IF(ISPICKVAL(Work_Overtime_Frequency__c,"Annually"), Work_Overtime_amount__c *1,0))))
CustomField.label: Annual Overtime Inome
